Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.41,0:38:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你可曾被人爱过  约翰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you ever been loved, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.06,0:38:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.83,0:38:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那你是不会明白的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then you wouldn't understand.
