Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.16,0:40:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,思想老派\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Old-fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.74,0:40:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是我的机器人也有停用的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even my robot's discontinued.
